{"article_id":"huarkCJcKEusc4TU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"During President Donald Trump ' s summit-ending news conference in Vietnam on Thursday , a reporter asked him","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"if he ' d confronted North Korean dictator Kim Jong Un about the treatment of Otto Warmbier ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"an American student","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"who was imprisoned in North Korea for 15 months ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"only to return to the US in a comatose state in June 2017","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"and never recover .","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"The reporter noted","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"despite Warmbier ' s brutal death ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Trump has called Kim \" my friend \"","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"and repeatedly boasted about their \" great relationship. \"","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"The journalist then asked him ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"\" Have you in Singapore","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"[ during the first Trump-Kim summit ]","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"or here confronted Kim Jong Un about Otto Warmbier ' s death ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"asked him to take responsibility ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"and what did he say to you ? \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Trump confirmed","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that he had -","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"but went on to say","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"he takes Kim ' s word for it","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that he had nothing","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"to do with it .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"\" I really believe","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"something very bad happened to [ Warmbier ] ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"and I don ' t think","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that the top leadership knew about it , \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"\" I don ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that [ Kim ] would ' ve allowed that to happen .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"It just wasn ' t in his advantage to allow that to happen .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"\" I did speak to [ Kim about Warmbier ] .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"He felt very badly .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"He knew the case very well ,","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"but he knew it later .","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"And , you know ,","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"you got a lot of people - big country , lot of people .","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"And in those prisons and those camps , you have a lot of people .","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"And some really bad things happened to Otto .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Some really , really bad things .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"But he tells me","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"that he didn ' t know about it","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"and I will take him at his word .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"WOW --","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Trump says","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"he does n't think","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Kim Jong Un is responsible for Otto Warmbier 's death .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"`` I do not think","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"the top leadership knew about it ...","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"I do not believe","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that he would have allowed that to happen ...","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"He tells me","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"he did now know about it","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"and I will take him at his word . ''","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"pic.twitter.com/mDydJGq2dv","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"- Aaron Rupar","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"( @ atrupar )","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"February 28 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"It ' s hard to imagine that North Korea ' s totalitarian dictator wasn ' t aware of how a high-profile captive was treated","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"- especially considering the show trial","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that Warmbier ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"who was arrested","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"for allegedly stealing a propaganda poster ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"was forced to endure .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"As has previously detailed ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"the North Korean government claimed","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Warmbier \" was left in a coma","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"because of a food poisoning disease","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"called botulism ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"but doctors were strangely unable to identify any trace of botulism or the cause of his deathly injuries . \"","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"American doctors were also unable to discover any physical evidence of abuse or torture","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"- despite the fact","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that Warmbier ' s parents had described in gruesome detail the horrific state","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"their son was in","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"when he ' d returned to the US .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"\" It looked like someone had taken a pair of pliers","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and re-arranged his bottom teeth , \"","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Warmbier ' s father Fred told GQ magazine .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Trump ' s comments","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"absolving Kim of responsibility for Warmbier ' s death","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"were widely criticized .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Rob Portman , a Republican US senator from Warmbier ' s home state of Ohio , released a statement","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"\" we should never let North Korea off the hook . \"","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Trump ' s former UN Ambassador Nikki Haley also seemed to subtly rebuke the president in a tweet .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Americans know the cruelty","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"that was placed on Otto Warmbier by the North Korean regime .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"Our hearts are with the Warmbier family for their strength and courage .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"We will never forget Otto .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"❤️","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"- Nikki Haley","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"( @ NikkiHaley )","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"February 28 , 2019","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"But one of the negotiators","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"who worked","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"to bring Warmbier home from North Korea","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"- Mickey Bergman of the Richardson Center -","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"told","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"he thought","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"he understood what Trump was trying to say , albeit in an ineloquent way .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"what","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"[ Trump ] was referring to is that Kim told him","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"he doesn ' t know what went wrong , \"","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Bergman said ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that \" whether we want to believe that or not \" is another question .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Bergman pointed out","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that it ' s unprecedented for a North Korean hostage to be returned to the US \" in a coma. \"","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Along the same lines , Bergman characterized the Warmbier tragedy as \" an anomaly \" during an interview earlier Thursday on Fox News .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"But Bergman also told","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that \" there is no doubt whatsoever in my mind and in anybody else ' s mind","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"that the North Koreans are absolutely responsible for the death of Otto Warmbier . \"","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"\" Whether it was intentional or an accident , \"","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"he continued ,","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"\" he was under their control or supervision ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"and the fact","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"that he was in the detention for more than a year in North Korea","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"I would argue","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"is torture in itself . \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Trump ' s comments","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"about believing Kim","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"when he says","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"he had nothing to do with Warmbier ' s death","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"echo comments","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"he ' s made","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"about Russian President Vladimir Putin and Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"( MBS ) .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"Though the US intelligence community concluded","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"that Russia meddled in the 2016 presidential election on Trump ' s behalf ,","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"Trump said during a joint news conference with Putin last July","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"that Putin \" was extremely strong and powerful in his denial \"","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"and hence \" I don ' t see any reason \"","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"to believe the US intelligence community over Putin ' s word .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Trump ' s comments were widely criticized ,","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"and he later said","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"he misspoke .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"while the US intelligence community concluded","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"the Saudi government was responsible for the murder of dissident journalist and US resident Jamal Khashoggi last fall ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Trump indicated","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"he ' s willing to take MBS ' s word for it","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"that he wasn ' t involved .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"... during the call ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"and told me","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"that he has already started ,","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"and will rapidly expand ,","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"a full and complete investigation into this matter .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Answers will be forthcoming shortly .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"October 16 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"During his news conference Thursday , Trump once again signaled a willingness","depth":4},{"id":153,"text":"to believe the word of an authoritarian over that of his own intelligence community .","depth":4},{"id":154,"text":"Asked about intelligence reports","depth":6},{"id":155,"text":"that North Korea has recently expanded its nuclear and missile programs ,","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"Trump responded","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"that he doesn ' t necessarily buy it .","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"\" Some people are saying that ,","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"and some people are denying that , \"","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"\" Some people are saying that","depth":6},{"id":162,"text":"and some people aren ' t . \"","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"The news moves fast .","depth":2},{"id":164,"text":"To stay updated ,","depth":3},{"id":165,"text":"follow Aaron Rupar on Twitter ,","depth":4},{"id":166,"text":"and read more of ' s policy and politics coverage .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":333,"left":329,"right":332,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":329,"left":318,"right":328,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":286,"right":317,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":224,"right":285,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":177,"right":223,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":172,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":0,"right":171,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":171,"left":1,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":2,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":3,"right":